00:03:40.190 --> 00:03:42.629
George Lucas Sells His Land to Charity

00:03:42.629 --> 00:03:45.680
George Lucas is one of those people who need
no introduction.

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:49.680
After all, he’s responsible for a couple
of famous films, some of which you might even

00:03:49.680 --> 00:03:53.319
have heard of, including Star Wars, Indiana
Jones, and E.T.

00:03:53.319 --> 00:03:58.209
For 25 years, Lucas had been attempting to
build a special effects workshop on his property

00:03:58.209 --> 00:04:03.480
in Marin County, California, which would revitalize
the area and create hundreds of high-paying

00:04:03.480 --> 00:04:04.480
jobs.

00:04:04.480 --> 00:04:08.300
But, he was thwarted by his rich neighbors
at every turn, all out of fear that such a

00:04:08.300 --> 00:04:12.970
development would bring ruinous traffic to
the area and cause so much light pollution

00:04:12.970 --> 00:04:17.930
that “their dark starry nights would be
destroyed” (actual quote, by the way.)

00:04:17.930 --> 00:04:20.489
So, in 2012, Lucas dropped those plans.

00:04:20.489 --> 00:04:23.270
And then immediately announced that he’d
sold the land to the Marin Community Foundation,

00:04:23.270 --> 00:04:27.470
all so they could finally build some much-needed
low-income housing.

00:04:27.470 --> 00:04:31.849
Predictably, Lucas’ neighbors went crazy
over that decision, but there was little they

00:04:31.849 --> 00:04:33.740
could do to stop it.

00:04:33.740 --> 00:04:34.740
5.

00:04:34.740 --> 00:04:36.940
Michael Crichton Gets Personal

00:04:36.940 --> 00:04:40.800
In 2004, author Michael Crichton published
“State of Fear,” a science-fiction work

00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:43.159
about global warming and environmental terrorism.

00:04:43.159 --> 00:04:47.279
However, whilst it proved to be a bestseller
amongst the general public, it was heavily

00:04:47.279 --> 00:04:52.139
criticized by the scientific community for
distorting evidence for global warming.

00:04:52.139 --> 00:04:56.349
One such critic was Michael Crowley who, in
an analysis of Crichton’s work, accused

00:04:56.349 --> 00:05:00.939
Crichton of being a negative influence on
the discussion of global warming and contributing

00:05:00.939 --> 00:05:06.069
to an increasingly hostile attitude towards
scientists who supported the idea of the phenomenon.

00:05:06.069 --> 00:05:10.830
Crichton wasn’t entirely happy with this
critique and made his displeasure quite obvious

00:05:10.830 --> 00:05:14.029
in his next work, confusingly titled “Next.”

00:05:14.029 --> 00:05:18.869
In several chapters, it features a character
named Mick Crowley, who is on trial for successfully

00:05:18.869 --> 00:05:21.759
raping a two year-old child despite having
a woefully small penis.

00:05:21.759 --> 00:05:25.650
We’d like to make it absolutely clear that’s
a part of the book; we aren’t joking or

00:05:25.650 --> 00:05:26.650
making any of that up.

00:05:26.650 --> 00:05:28.779
You can even read the extract in question
here.

00:05:28.779 --> 00:05:29.779
