00:05:29.779 --> 00:05:30.909
House Gets Colorful Paint Job

00:05:30.909 --> 00:05:34.960
The Westboro Baptist Church has rightfully
earned the reputation of being a horrible

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:37.150
organization populated by horrible people.

00:05:37.150 --> 00:05:40.970
Spearheaded by Fred Phelps, the church is
vehemently homophobic, being responsible for

00:05:40.970 --> 00:05:46.199
the sadly-famous “God Hates Fags” signs
which are proudly displayed by the group at

00:05:46.199 --> 00:05:52.919
funerals of military personnel, gay people,
and just about anybody else who isn’t them.

00:05:52.919 --> 00:05:56.849
In 2013, however, the group must have received
quite a shock when they turned up for their

00:05:56.849 --> 00:06:01.590
weekly gay-bashing rituals only to find the
house across the street had been re-painted

00:06:01.590 --> 00:06:04.610
… into the colors of the LGBT flag.

00:06:04.610 --> 00:06:06.490
This was the work of one man, Aaron Jackson.

00:06:06.490 --> 00:06:11.039
Whilst looking on Google Earth in March, he
spotted the property for sale and decided

00:06:11.039 --> 00:06:16.629
to spend $83,000 establishing a HQ for his
anti-bullying organisation in possibly the

00:06:16.629 --> 00:06:18.770
world’s most ironic location.

00:06:18.770 --> 00:06:22.839
That might sound like a lot of money for some
passive-aggressive payback, but since trolling

00:06:22.839 --> 00:06:29.680
bigots in a manner they can do absolutely
nothing about is priceless, it’s money well-spent.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:31.009
3.

00:06:31.009 --> 00:06:34.159
Bank of America Gets (Legally) Foreclosed

00:06:34.159 --> 00:06:38.860
In 2011, Bank of America delivered a foreclosure
notice on a family’s home for the heinous

00:06:38.860 --> 00:06:41.499
crime of defaulting on their mortgage.

00:06:41.499 --> 00:06:46.159
Only one problem: the family in question owned
the house outright, as they’d bought it

00:06:46.159 --> 00:06:47.159
in cash.

00:06:47.159 --> 00:06:51.190
They didn’t even have a mortgage, let alone
one with Bank of America.

00:06:51.190 --> 00:06:54.970
The matter was later taken to court, and ended
with the family winning their case and Bank

00:06:54.970 --> 00:07:00.360
of America being ordered to pay them $2,534
restitution for their legal costs.

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:04.689
Of course, BoA refused to pay the money, because
it was founded by Satan.

00:07:04.689 --> 00:07:06.270
So the family got creative.

00:07:06.270 --> 00:07:09.849
After consulting with their lawyers, the family
appeared at the bank one day and – armed

00:07:09.849 --> 00:07:14.039
with a removal truck and a couple of sheriff’s
deputies – foreclosed on it.

00:07:14.039 --> 00:07:18.729
As in, they were legally allowed to strip
the bank bare (including of all the money

00:07:18.729 --> 00:07:20.300
in the tellers’ drawers).

00:07:20.300 --> 00:07:24.139
The bank manager was suddenly able to pay
the family after all, presenting them with

00:07:24.139 --> 00:07:26.020
a check an hour later.

00:07:26.020 --> 00:07:27.020
